Usage:
      mpl OPTION [SONG]
      mpl OPTION [PLAYLIST]
      mpl OPTION [PLAYLIST] -u [URL]

      OPTIONS:
      -h                    :display help menu
      -l PLAYLIST           :display all songs in PLAYLIST
      -L                    :display all available PLAYLISTS
      -e PLAYLIST           :edit the PLAYLIST file
      -c PLAYLIST           :create new empty playlist PLAYLIST
      -p PLAYLIST           :play PLAYLIST

      -c PLIST -u URL       :create new playlist PLAYLIST from url URL
                              ... url should be a youtube or soundcloud playlist url
